pages.text:
Kirk Adams
Kirk Adams has etched his name into the hearts of audiences and critics nationwide, leaving an indelible mark on the music scene. A revered figure in the vibrant Tampa Bay music community, Kirk's compositions resonate with a potent blend of melancholy, resounding guitars, and irresistible melodies. Seamlessly weaving tales that are poignant, humorous, contemplative, eerie, and occasionally all of the above within a single song, Kirk captivates listeners with his multifaceted artistry. Dive into his world, where every note carries a story waiting to unfold.
https://www.kirkadamsmusic.com/
Branson Welsh
The Branson Welsh Group is a heavy hitting, high energized Blues Rock 'n' Soul act from St. Petersburg , FL. The group is led by frontman /guitarist/singer Branson Welsh and has shared the stage with top national acts such as Eric Gales, Hubert Sumlin and Damon Fowler to name a few.
Family Funk Jam
Funk/Soul/Fusion band from St Pete. Hosts of The Family Funk Jam every Sunday 10-2am
Nathan Mitchell
Nathan Mitchell, is an accomplished American contemporary jazz/soul (composer, producer, and multi-instrumentalist) music educator and humanitarian. A Grammy Nominated, 3x NAACP Image Award-nominated, and BILLBOARD charting artist with 10 top 30 BILLBOARD hits including three #1 BILLBOARD songs; has become one of the most respected “musical storytellers” in the contemporary jazz industry. This award-nominated and winning artist is known best for his electric showmanship, unique talents, and enthusiastic energy.
https://www.nathanmitchellmusic.com/home
Shawn Brown
Shawn Brown was born to James Brown and Shirley Brown on November the 13, 1962, he was the last of six siblings. Shirley Brown was a classically trained pianist and vocalist. James Brown was a chief/jazz vocalist in the United States Navy. This union produced a solid foundation as all of his siblings were musically nurtured and encouraged to pursue their talents. His brother, Hiram Brown, shared the same talents and mentored Shawn to become the entertainer he is today. Shirley Browns spiritual motivations embraced all of her family and grounded them with Christian convictions and a strong faith.
https://shawnbrownentertainment.com/
Seth Campbell
Seth Campbell is a talented musician, singer, and songwriter based out of St. Petersburg, FL.
​
His live performance blends flavors of 70s rock and roll, alternative and pop, for a dynamic and energetic soul ride.
Expect powerful vocals, hot guitar solos and impressive showmanship!
"The former America’s Got Talent contestant is now relentlessly gigging throughout the greater Tampa area, playing both original songs and fun covers. His music blends the genres of rock, blues, jazz and folk in a neat, guitar-heavy package. His sets are known to be interactive and upbeat..."
​
-Kyla Fields of Creative Loafing Tampa
www.sethcmusic.com/home
